{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-entries-markdown-remark-parent-file-relative-directory-markdown-remark-parent-file-name-jsx","path":"/entries/algorithms/voronoi-tesselation/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Voronoi Tessellation","type":"algorithm"},"html":"<h1>Voronoi Tessellation</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; margin-left: 0!important; margin-right: 0!important;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A portrait created using Voronoi Tessellation\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/GenerativeArtArchive/static/22041a64e11de28c472fa70727af0a66/5a190/sns.png\"\n        srcset=\"/GenerativeArtArchive/static/22041a64e11de28c472fa70727af0a66/772e8/sns.png 200w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/22041a64e11de28c472fa70727af0a66/e17e5/sns.png 400w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/22041a64e11de28c472fa70727af0a66/5a190/sns.png 800w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/22041a64e11de28c472fa70727af0a66/c1b63/sns.png 1200w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/22041a64e11de28c472fa70727af0a66/29007/sns.png 1600w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/22041a64e11de28c472fa70727af0a66/6052f/sns.png 2030w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Image credit: <a href=\"https://www.flong.com/archive/projects/zoo/index.html\">Golan Levin, from Segmentation and Symptom</a></p>\n<h2>Overview</h2>\n<p>Voronoi tessellations are geometric patterns that mimic structures we often see in nature, like the way cells or crystals are formed. These patterns emerge when different areas of space find balance, each centered around a point. In computer art, Voronoi tessellations are used as a way to divide space into regions based on an arbitrary set of points, known as \"sites.\" Each region contains all the points closest to its site, creating a patchwork of shapes. This process is especially popular in generative art because it produces interesting, organic-looking designs that can resemble natural forms or abstract geometric compositions.</p>\n<h2>How it works</h2>\n<p>Starting in a 2D plane like a square or rectangle:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Seed the space with <em>n</em> points. These will be the centers of the different regions.</li>\n<li>For every point on the plane, measure how far it is from each of the seeds.</li>\n<li>Each point on the plane is assigned to its closest seed. All the points closest to a particular seed form that seed's region (or Voronoi cell).</li>\n<li>Draw straight lines that separate the different seed regions. The result will be <em>n</em> regions that fit together like puzzle pieces.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Examples</h2>\n<p>This example shows different coloured Voronoi cells with their associated seed points:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; margin-left: 0!important; margin-right: 0!important;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Voronoi tessellation with seeds\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/GenerativeArtArchive/static/2da95cde202d6edaa16f133dc3a5a926/01e7c/voronoi-seeds-small.png\"\n        srcset=\"/GenerativeArtArchive/static/2da95cde202d6edaa16f133dc3a5a926/772e8/voronoi-seeds-small.png 200w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/2da95cde202d6edaa16f133dc3a5a926/e17e5/voronoi-seeds-small.png 400w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/2da95cde202d6edaa16f133dc3a5a926/01e7c/voronoi-seeds-small.png 512w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Here we see a plane in a 3D environment, with a Voronoi pattern:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; margin-left: 0!important; margin-right: 0!important;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3D voronoi plane\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/GenerativeArtArchive/static/859b1312307c31b0e628bb51891b2918/5a190/voronoi-plane.png\"\n        srcset=\"/GenerativeArtArchive/static/859b1312307c31b0e628bb51891b2918/772e8/voronoi-plane.png 200w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/859b1312307c31b0e628bb51891b2918/e17e5/voronoi-plane.png 400w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/859b1312307c31b0e628bb51891b2918/5a190/voronoi-plane.png 800w,\n/GenerativeArtArchive/static/859b1312307c31b0e628bb51891b2918/2bef9/voronoi-plane.png 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>"}},"pageContext":{"id":"d12663d8-254b-5541-8389-d36055e2c778","parent__relativeDirectory":"algorithms/voronoi-tesselation","parent__name":"index","__params":{"parent__relativeDirectory":"algorithms","parent__name":"voronoi-tesselation"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1624980200","2806632227","37672888","4259328202"],"slicesMap":{}}